<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.2">
<l>mūva rākiya mūrtti yaimutaṉ mūvark kumutal vaṉṟaṉṉaic</l>
<l>cāva muḷḷaṉa nīkku vāṉait taṭanka ṭalkiṭan tāṉṟaṉṉait</l>
<l>tēva tēvaṉait teṉṉi laṅkai yeriyeḻac ceṟṟa villiyaip</l>
<l>pāva nācaṉaip paṅka yattaṭaṅ kaṇṇa ṉaippara vumiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The form that is the Three, the first one of the primeval Three,</l>
<l>the one who repels those that are on the bow, the one who lies on the vast ocean,</l>
<l>the god of gods, the bowman who destroyed southern Laṅka so it went up in flame,</l>
<l>the destroyer of evil, Kṛṣṇa with broad lotus eyes rever.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
